like":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"溫子仁我屌你女友！"},{"pid":"0b4cd78ea4148b380349d3dd131b2f18489adf4e","tid":952244,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:49:36.000Z","msg":"導演夫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902ed2eb03d89ec3bcda70f125f36e04d1290cb9","tid":952244,"uid":171058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a545c348c88812662c8f76784ead58060124bab8","tid":952244,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"本年唯一DC漫畫電影《水行俠》（Aquaman）將於下周上映，導演溫子仁（James Wan）脫離恐怖題材，首次挑戰超級英雄作品便獲得不俗評價，成功為DC挽回面子。<br />\n<br />\n一向行事低調的溫子仁，平日絕少提及私生活，但原來他有位影星女友Ingrid Bisu，不時結伴出席公開活動，呢位靚女友仲有份參演早前上映的鬼片《詭修女》（The Nun），似乎都靠身為監製兼編劇的溫子仁穿針引線。<br />\n<br />\n現年31歲的Ingrid Bisu出生於羅馬尼亞，是德國與羅馬尼亞混血兒，擁有標緻五官及火辣身材，16歲時獲發掘當雜誌模特兒，成為她加入影圈的契機。入行初期，Ingrid Bisu演出羅馬尼亞電視劇，2005年演出首部電影《嗜血黑天使》（Blood Rayne）。<br />\n<br />\n入行多年，Ingrid Bisu基本上沒甚代表作，較出名的作品包括曾入圍奧斯卡最佳外語片的《爸不得妳快樂》（Toni Erdmann），飾演女主角的辦公室助理，以及於今年上映的《詭修女》中扮演Oana修女，或許令她最出名的是成為溫子仁的女友。不過溫子仁與Ingrid Bisu絕少提及對方，只間中在社交網站上載合照，相當低調。<br />\n<br />\nIngrid Bisu有份參演《詭修女》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5guVR2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5guVR2.png&h=f02b16b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VTF7Hw3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVTF7Hw3.png&h=f23b9053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saGuVR3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsaGuVR3.png&h=452a422c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ufyMX5p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FufyMX5p.png&h=2ef35951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1rR9b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1rR9b4.png&h=da906528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctdX4Lq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctdX4Lq.png&h=72bf286f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjEMdDM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjEMdDM.png&h=cfdbac0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMEwpLs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMEwpLs.png&h=ab049a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8BOrYO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8BOrYO.png&h=0d99e621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rtDk2w9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrtDk2w9.png&h=7bb9f480&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:12:06.000Z","msg":"睇過"},{"pid":"13bc4fe054e0f2a5eafdc1269f4d2e77431cbad1","tid":952244,"uid":176929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我到直以為James wan 係gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8c4a68a357716c4bd99a0f18167b4b9d32a942","tid":952244,"uid":135689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:15:45.000Z","msg":"不嬲有優點先有人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通吼啲乜撚都冇既連登仔先係清泉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地又唔係私銅臭"},{"pid":"90f2e0e38e834a9ff4db1968a5448d3367446405","tid":952244,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">馬來西亞人係咁高架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"7c75709fd0d70aa24c0e6402de95ba794db4c9eb","tid":952244,"uid":108816,"like":0,"disli